snippet.textDisplay:
Been almost 10 years listening to this masterpiece. Was single back in 2015 and somehow still could feel the pain as depicted in the song. Fast forward to 2021 - got blessed with the most beautiful daughter in world. Day 1 of her getting birth - listened to this and couldn’t stop tears. 

And now it’s may 2025 - my daughter, wife and son have gone to their in laws for a few days in ludhiana while there is blackout there. Damn missing them so much while listening to this!
